Title: Fix disappearance of popup indicator when reloading graphs
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1612256914
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b6

The indicator popup that is shown if you hover above a graph was missing after
the regularly page reload.

The indicator will now persist, even after this reload.
